Class ExtensibleList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, List<E>, RandomAccess, IList<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractTreeIterator, ExtensibleList.FastCompare, ExtensibleList.UnmodifiableEList, NotifyingList, UniqueExtensibleList

    public class ExtensibleList<E>
extends AbstractList<E>
implements IList<E>, RandomAccess, Cloneable, Serializable
    A highly extensible list implementation.
